# WhatsNext

A "What's next" link list, styled to mirror the Hugo `whatsnext` shortcode. Use it at the bottom of a page to point readers at related docs.

The component has two parts:

- `WhatsNext` ‚Äî the container with an optional description and a list wrapper.
- `NextLink` ‚Äî a single link row, with optional trailing tag.

## WhatsNext properties

| Property | Type     | Default                                                  | Description                                                                 |
|----------|----------|----------------------------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| `desc`   | `string` | `Additional helpful documentation, links, and articles:` | Lead-in sentence above the list. Pass an empty string to omit it entirely.  |

## NextLink properties

| Property | Type     | Default | Description                                                                                              |
|----------|----------|---------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| `href`   | `string` | ‚Äî       | Required. The URL the link points to.                                                                    |
| `tag`    | `string` | ‚Äî       | Optional. A short trailing badge (rendered uppercase). Hidden on narrow viewports (under 576px), as in Hugo. |

The default slot holds the link text. Anything inline is allowed (icons, badges, formatted text).

## Examples

### Default description

{% tabs %}
{% tab label="Result" %}
{% whatsNext %}
{% nextLink href="/api/latest/dashboards/" %}List dashboards{% /nextLink %}
{% nextLink href="/api/latest/monitors/" tag="guide" %}Manage monitors{% /nextLink %}
{% nextLink href="/api/latest/logs/" %}Search logs{% /nextLink %}
{% /whatsNext %}
{% /tab %}
{% tab label="Markdoc" %}
```markdoc
{% whatsNext %}
{% nextLink href="/api/latest/dashboards/" %}List dashboards{% /nextLink %}
{% nextLink href="/api/latest/monitors/" tag="guide" %}Manage monitors{% /nextLink %}
{% nextLink href="/api/latest/logs/" %}Search logs{% /nextLink %}
{% /whatsNext %}
```
{% /tab %}
{% /tabs %}

### Custom description

{% tabs %}
{% tab label="Result" %}
{% whatsNext desc="To learn more about Datadog APM:" %}
{% nextLink href="/tracing/" %}Trace your applications{% /nextLink %}
{% nextLink href="/tracing/setup/" tag="setup" %}APM setup{% /nextLink %}
{% /whatsNext %}
{% /tab %}
{% tab label="Markdoc" %}
